{"tid":1686291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[輸出革命] 知乎講起樓價彈出撐港言論 提議組成網軍","createTime":"2019-11-01T04:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T08:36:17.000Z","uid":226562,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec335d9efeb69bfdc432a84d0f0c8a8d79bbc9f9","tid":1686291,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"話說知乎講起 房價讓現在的年輕人有多絕望？<br />\n<br />\n即刻無數明白人言論彈出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放幾條link先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/347845593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F347845593&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=58cb925f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/347845593</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/7363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F7363&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=3131f00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/7363</a><br />\n<br />\n精選評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 請看香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 如果百姓安居樂業，也不會被境外勢力輕易蠱惑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 能吃好喝好住好，傻子才鬧。 哪個國家能鼓動美國民眾? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 中國有這麼好搞亂，是誰的問題，你去搞亂美國試試？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 美國能煽動一兩百多萬人啊。 你去美國看看能煽動怎麼多人不？ 你這種傢伙就是把頭埋在沙子裡，裝作什麼問題都沒有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 有些事情確實是有原因的，你看到別人亂，罵他們廢青，殊不知你如果處於那個環境，你可能比他們更廢青。<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 大陸有退路，大不了大城市賺錢老家買房，高貴自由的香港年輕人死也不會退到大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（已刪）<br />\n&gt; 當代中國年輕人不會絕望，相反，他們會生活得越來越好，因為他們正在慢慢學會不買房，不生小孩，不贍養老人，消費主義，及時行樂，極端利己主義，唯利是圖。當你背負了不能承受的責任和&ldquo;應該&rdquo;，拋棄掉後自己就能生活得很好，你會怎麼選？恕我直言，中國的年輕人永遠不可能被高房價毀掉，被高房價毀掉的只能是中國本身。房價出現恐慌性拋售的苗頭，國家尚能政治干預。而年輕人的夢想如果岀現恐慌性拋售，整個民族的潛力都會直接跌停。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議組成香城網軍部<br />\n連埋品蔥反賊出嚟入去帶風向<br />\n<br />\n唔使做得好明顯<br />\n例如可以出 港警對待廢青的方式比起公安是不是太溫和了？<br />\n然後放晒兩邊警暴證據入去"},{"pid":"c86053a60fc3fbeef10ebf3139c88439d2e01fb4","tid":1686291,"uid":226562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"甴近平<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復中華 驅逐共匪"},{"pid":"0d47b2f420cf80b7f66ba23928e73029f28f3d41","tid":1686291,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"甴近平<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復中華 驅逐共匪"},{"pid":"e32b237e52b9f9fd3db7198773c5b9be265be2f0","tid":1686291,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"甴近平<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n光復中華 驅逐共匪"},{"pid":"24df2839168334774b3181f2e2ba289a536f0529","tid":1686291,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"b8241e187edf028a1c3057a5cdcc40e565f8f3d7","tid":1686291,"uid":171849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"算吧啦<br />\n知乎班韭菜當年咪講過修憲唔好<br />\n被del cm之後好快又講愛國<br />\n收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n之前NBA出共彈出又彈入<br />\n夠有人批評d人唔愛國仲睇NBA啦<br />\n咪又係俾人del cm<br />\n最後又係睇返NBA<br />\n甚麼事都沒有發生<br />\n<br />\n你要明白<br />\n大部份知乎用戶都係二三線城市既人<br />\n佢地讀書